HEADWORD: Epispadias
<hw>Ep`i*spa"di*as</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., fr.
Gr. <grk>'epi`</grk> upon + <?/ to draw, rend.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>A deformity in which the urethra opens upon the top of the penis,
instead of at its extremity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

